{"tid":1324702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再比文宣po沉，推起佢。各位和理非入一入黎，星期六一齊文宣遍地開花","createTime":"2019-07-16T15:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:11:30.000Z","uid":280725,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"07e8c1308672a0a0c8dfeb2099ccfd185fee9f95","tid":1324702,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想去自己個區連儂牆坐底擺booth同人辯論</span><br />\n類似呢D咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGWXjN6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGWXjN6.png&h=aa1e5c47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本人星期六會去自己區個到做<br />\n唔使攞枱都得<br />\n坐係地下擺紙皮牌係隔離同人講命題同規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n認真我真係和理非到走火入魔<br />\n不過我仲係覺得只要可以說服一個人都值得<br />\n大家覺得自己唔會拗輸比人可以一齊做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊星期六出黎自己個區連儂牆<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">比大家見到公理何在</span></span><br />\n<br />\n記住唔好人身攻擊 要真係理論<br />\n同見有藍絲激動 可以幫口說理<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但千其唔好激動過佢</span><br />\n呢個都係形象工程<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">千其唔好主動郁手</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0f7b7cb7eba9ee13711b68be6b162c97023629a2","tid":1324702,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:40:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d8ac2766d3ed455e26dad1030109fc320bbd1f0","tid":1324702,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:40:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da4afe0485c29aba10d21fe5fe74ba7b7d8127ce","tid":1324702,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:41:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"277676976bb1a899e6a903b8ab2367e10cecc28c","tid":1324702,"uid":280725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f01113c8a380130aaf77e6059e18128908716e3","tid":1324702,"uid":89974,"like":3,"dislike